*"On je rekao da će biti tu večeras." (He said he would be there tonight.)
*"Šta je on rekao? " (What did he say?)
*"Kako je rekao da se to radi? " (How did he say to do that?)
*"Rekao je da će se vratiti za pet minuta." (He said he would be back in five minutes.)
*"Šta je ona rekla? " (What did she say?)
*"Ona je rekla da će biti tu za pola sata." (She said she would be there in half an hour.)